com.microsoft.windowsazure.services.blob.models

Class GetBlobPropertiesResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.windowsazure.services.blob.models.GetBlobPropertiesResult

  • public class GetBlobPropertiesResult
extends java.lang.Object
    A wrapper class for the response returned from a Blob Service REST API Get Blob Properties operation. This is returned by calls to implementations of BlobContract.getBlobProperties(String, String) and BlobContract.getBlobProperties(String, String, GetBlobPropertiesOptions) .

    See the Get Blob Properties documentation on MSDN for details of the underlying Blob Service REST API operation.
